{{wikipedia}}
==English==

===Etymology===
Shortening of [[periwig]], itself an alteration of French ''[[perruque]]''.

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪɡ|-ɪɡ]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A head of real or [[synthetic]] hair worn on the head to [[disguise]] [[baldness]]; for cultural or religious reasons; for [[fashion]]; or by [[actor]]s to help them resemble the character they are [[portray]]ing.

====Synonyms====
*[[hairpiece]]
*[[toupee]], [[toupe]]
*[[peruke]]

====Derived terms====
*[[wig out]]
*[[bald wig]]
*[[fright wig]]

