{{bottom}}

===Verb===
{{en-verb|wigg|ing}}
# To put on a wig; to provide with a wig (especially of an actor etc.).
# ''(colloquial)'' To [[upbraid]], [[reprimand]].
# ''(colloquial)'' To become very excitable or emotional; to lose control of one's emotions.

